# Pump TMA — Project Skills

Before implementing or researching in this repo, read and follow the matching skill in `.cursor/skills/`:

| Task | Skill |
|------|-------|
| Docs, APIs, versions, current web facts | `research-verified` |
| Design system, tokens, nav, layout specs | `pump-tma-design-system` |
| Pages, modals, forms, styling, trading UI | `pump-tma-ui-ux` |
| App Router pages, API routes, PostgreSQL layer | `pump-tma-nextjs` |
| wagmi, viem, RainbowKit, on-chain writes | `pump-tma-web3` |

## Defaults

- **UI work:** Read `pump-tma-design-system` first, then `pump-tma-ui-ux`. Top nav + mobile bottom bar — no left sidebar.
- Verify library APIs via Context7 (`user-context7`) — do not guess versions or syntax.
- Match existing patterns in `src/` before introducing new libraries or UI primitives.
- No shadcn/MUI; use `globals.css` component classes and `pump-*` tokens.
- Dev server: `npm run dev` on port **3012**.
